Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世學姐的蹂躪式進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也請來蹂躪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世…學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是愛國者爆炸扣殺啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學 學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路她絕對也是想在社團活動中揮灑青春的汗水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對吧 千夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想她應該是去看理世的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}畢竟一直都在打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:01:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去邀請下紗路如何？ 她一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說的也是啊 我去邀請看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想參加社團活動看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是厭倦了我們店的工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在Rabbit House進行社團活動如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請快去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}社團活動 真是令人懷念的話語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難道青山小姐曾經是文藝社的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有個整天叮囑我一定要遵守截稿日的嚴格的後輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}從那時候開始就經常拖稿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}當時煩惱了好久 是選文藝社還是吹箭社好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吹箭！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吹箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我奶奶是吹箭高手 以前還一起玩過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路她吹得特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}既然有飛鏢咖啡店的話 開個吹箭咖啡店感覺也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}至少換成飛鏢啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要 要我也一起去社團幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去人手不足的社團當幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會不會拖後腿啊 有點擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是陪著練習而已 放輕鬆好好享受就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}馬尾辮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家都說這樣威風凜凜的比較像我的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}風格？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就像是在和擊垮社員的狂暴黑馬對峙一樣 十分有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是練習而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}上了哦 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要上了 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}所謂的特賣會就是賣給特別的你這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是美妙的話語啊 特賣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能行嗎 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐 庶民研究社的那些人完全張冠李戴了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}社團活動的日程表排太滿了 讓我來管理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}麻煩你了 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}馬術社之後是服裝社 三十分鐘以後是吹箭社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世學姐好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到各種社團幫忙 就好像傳說中的那位大人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 那個我有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 那位大人是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼 那位大人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}據我打聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}神出鬼沒 過去曾給許多社團提出了適當的建議並引導他們走向勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}其名為 Miss.翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\be3\pos(743,650)}<Emerald>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}翠 翠星？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要不要在幫社團忙之時 順便收集一下那個人的情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}才貌雙全 文武雙全 肯定和理世學姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒 沒有興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒有啊 只要紗路開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Miss.翠星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過直接告訴你就沒什麼樂趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓我們來比比誰能搭配出最適合理世穿的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比賽！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}適合理世學姐穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幹勁十足啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要是你輸了就得穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 這樣的怎麼穿得出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}會被媽媽罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到 到底是怎樣的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是我們很難穿上身的 很過激的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}跟Fleur沒太大區別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那先從服裝社做的衣服開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 學姐你好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}薔薇和炸彈的守護者降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}技 技術的差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還沒開戰就知道我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不戰而敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}輸掉比賽的紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就像是洋娃娃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}反正我都習慣這樣的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這衣服不是挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Miss.翠星石的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要是你贏了遊戲我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們也太喜歡搞比賽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}相對的 要是我們贏了你就入社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太容易了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這條件這麼簡單的就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}射標靶這事我在射擊訓練的時候就輕車熟路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我來把分數拉開 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}意外的好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 輪到紗路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要是不由我來力挽狂瀾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世學姐就得加入吹箭社了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}連學姐都輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}抱歉啊 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}根本贏不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}噗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}巧合而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我把標靶換小點的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明 明明還沒攝取什麼咖啡因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我竟然有如此之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好厲害啊 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}多 多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這技術完全能把你推薦進特種部隊裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然挺高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過我還是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說 我們的比賽目的是啥來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是有關翠小姐的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}翠小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難道這是Miss.翠星石的本名？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}唔 其實我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過有聽說她是文藝社的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}文藝社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}聽說她有去各種社團串門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過好像有一個總能把她拽回來的後輩在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有那樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再來吹一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 來雪恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還在勸誘嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}想得到的情報已經得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}接下來的戰鬥已經毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗 紗路？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到頭來Miss.翠星石的本尊還是個謎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難到以後你都要綁這個髮型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一被說到這樣適合我 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我倒是非常喜歡你平時綁雙馬尾的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我可是看盡學姐各種姿態的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}帥的也好 可愛的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}全部都是理世學姐你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也挺想偶爾看到學姐綁馬尾時的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天反而是我各種被引導各種被搭救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}簡直就像是傳說中的翠小姐一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路看上去很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我有事想找你幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能幫到理世學姐的忙我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}多虧你才能弄得這麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看著心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想像她一樣讓大家都開開心心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你回來啦 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜 你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世學姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}下次大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是心愛說要給紗路你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能再來一杯藍山咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃 續杯麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 青山小姐 你的本名是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是BlueMountain吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對於大家來說 我就是青山BlueMountain…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}找到你了 青山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是我的責任編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然聯絡不上你 你就在Rabbit House
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}散漫的樣子從高中以來就完全沒變！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 別假裝聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不要做無謂的抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快點寫原稿 青山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}小翠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來是翠小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}截稿日都已經過了一週了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}假裝聽不見也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我珍藏至今的瓶中船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對於假日來說真是再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智～乃 來～玩～吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是個好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}去抓蟲子怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好不容易的假日 一個人的話太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把我當替身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好累
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}打工排得太滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還要為明天做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗～路～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不好好休息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來～玩～吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}會死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和我玩就會？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼樣 適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}甘兔庵浴衣週
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛也一副夏天的打扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜是不能來玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對不起 不過現在還是有點太心急…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是捕蟲籠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哎呀 很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世的話一定能理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理～世～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來～玩～吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3\an8}等等等 請別按了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大小姐正在忙著做明天的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}準備什麼啊 戰爭？ 好啊 算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是 你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}總之 今天不行的 請你一個人好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明培育士兵就要靠戰場才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哎呀 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能稍微 陪我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐也很閒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,600,0,,{\be3}終於找到你了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.51,Default,,100,0,0,,{\be3}那個 我是心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不小心撞到後靈魂互…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 我台詞還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}截稿日已經過了兩週又三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}拿著這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咖啡機？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用這個 支援一下智乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用微笑支援她 就是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智～乃～ 幫你泡咖啡來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}改變模式了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智～乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想在今天做完 別讓我分心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我特意拿來給你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛做好明天的準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們在這集合做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 還穿著睡衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快點換衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天開始要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}山裡玩的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我的心情傳達給大家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你在說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世邀請我們今天和明天去山裡玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世的邀請？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}收到邀請信了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}邀請信？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我沒有收到什麼邀請信…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明我邀請的時候就無人理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世的一句話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的 大家欺負人 真是的真是的真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛變得跟牛一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.15,Default,,400,0,0,,{\be3}我要閉門不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,300,0,,{\be3}回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 要出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛好像不知道今天的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不會吧 難道只有心愛沒收到邀請信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我還以為都收到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 收是收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就這麼放在制服的口袋裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是沒看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是為何如此生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺昨天心愛好像來約過我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也是忙著做瓶中船沒太理她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 心愛 願你早點消消氣快點出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還是得有人犧牲一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}犧牲一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只 只要你肯開門 我就任你撫摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那好 一個一個地進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}全員都要進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我先來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別急 惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這不是你能應付的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}求…求你了快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛不在我都坐立不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也是 沒有心愛的話我也想不出這樣的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過還是我最喜歡心愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也最喜歡大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那就快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們該做點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對口相聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心 心愛 來～玩～吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我不可能真的生大家氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真受不了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 智乃 在室外就別玩室內的遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不行哦 我沒收囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}小木屋是什麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}會很大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}會是什麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說起來我還是頭一次走出這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}由爺爺和爸爸看家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我能適應戶外活動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}彷彿提比在身邊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.25,Default,,300,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,200,0,,{\be3}我解開這道字謎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 又完成了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}山…是什麼樣的地方呢？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好可怕
